title: Eddie May Have Coronavirus + Bobby's TV Show Update + Brett Eldredge Talking About Love
itunes:title: Eddie May Have Coronavirus + Bobby's TV Show Update + Brett Eldredge Talking About Love
description:
We check in with Eddie who has been out this week after having coronavirus symptoms. He reveals a new symptom leading us to think he may have caught something down in Florida. Bobby gives us a not so great update about filming his new TV show. Plus, Brett Eldredge stops by the studio to talk about his new album and how he took some time to find out who he is and open himself up to love.
